            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><b>Subject matter and legislative competence of devolved legislatures</b></span></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num><span style="color:#000000">50 </span></num>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">There is no matter in the Act that is within the legislative competence of the devolved legislatures.</span></p>
