                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-09-14/debates/AFE1AEDC-E1B4-4287-9AF2-BEBCA0F7BF91/HealthAndSocialCareLevyBill#840" title=""><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>Vol. 700 Col. 840</u></span></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Public Bill Committee</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>14 September 2021</p>
                </td>
                <td>
