                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Report and Third Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>14 September 2021</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-09-14/debates/379AC113-D248-4B5D-B50B-C6839E4257AE/HealthAndSocialCareLevyBill#941" title=""><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>Vol. 700 Col. 941</u></span></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p><i>House of Lords</i></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Introduction</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>15 September 2021</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2021-09-15/debates/B572CADC-6EF7-4FEE-8888-C932380AB27D/HealthAndSocialCareLevyBill"><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>Vol. 814 Col. 1392</u></span></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Second Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>11 October 2021</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2021-10-11/debates/D8582F1D-578F-4996-A1C7-EF2E891C30B1/HealthAndSocialCareLevyBill"><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>Vol. 814 Col. 1657</u></span></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Order of Commitment discharged</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>11 October 2021</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2021-10-11/debates/D8582F1D-578F-4996-A1C7-EF2E891C30B1/HealthAndSocialCareLevyBill"><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>Vol. 814 Col. 1716</u></span></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Third Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>11 October 2021</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2021-10-11/debates/D8582F1D-578F-4996-A1C7-EF2E891C30B1/HealthAndSocialCareLevyBill"><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>Vol. 814 Col. 1716</u></span></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td rowspan="2">
                  <p>Royal Assent</p>
